## Acknowledgments

The Flatpak manifest structure for the base runtime is inspired by the
org.winehq.Wine Flatpak (https://github.com/flathub/org.winehq.Wine).

## Bundled Components

- Wine: LGPL-2.1-or-later (https://www.winehq.org/)
- Wine Gecko: MPL-1.1 or GPL-2.0+ or LGPL-2.0+ (https://gitlab.winehq.org/wine/wine/-/wikis/Gecko/)
- Wine Mono: GPL-2.0+ and LGPL-2.1 and MIT and MS-PL (https://gitlab.winehq.org/wine/wine/-/wikis/wine-mono/)
- Gamescope: BSD-2-Clause (https://github.com/ValveSoftware/gamescope)
- Samba: GPL-3.0-or-later (https://www.samba.org/)
- Kerberos (krb5): MIT (https://web.mit.edu/kerberos/)
- UnixODBC: LGPL-2.1 (http://www.unixodbc.org/)
- Zenity: LGPL-2.0+ (https://wiki.gnome.org/Projects/Zenity)
- 7-Zip: LGPL-2.1 and BSD-3-Clause (https://www.7-zip.org/)
- Individual games: Retain their original licenses (usually proprietary)
